node.text: August is the beginning of the turn towards darkness 🌚☀️🌹It’s almost time to say goodbye to nature’s bounty. By expressing your gratitude for your blessings in a ceremonial way, you invite more to follow. Prepare for the long farewell to summer with me as I read an excerpt from my Book of Blessings and Rituals, available on Amazon and all major bookstores.

node.title: The Book of Blessings & Rituals - A Reading with Athena Perrakis

node.text:
Are you ready to explore your spirituality and step into your full potential? 🦋🌙

Join Soul Shift Alchemize to expand your personal power, deepen your inner wisdom, and manifest joy, prosperity, and confidence. This online program will help you shift your mindset, so you feel more aligned and excited about your life and your future.

Alchemy is a process of transforming one substance, state of being, thought form, or creation into another. Alchemy is the process of becoming YOU – fully, passionately, and unapologetically.

It's never too late to start your healing journey, visit the link in bio to learn more and sign up for Soul Shift Alchemize.

node.text:
Are you seeing angel numbers? 😇 🔢 ✨ When the angels are communicating and attempting to get your attention, you will begin noticing repeating and sequential numbers such as 444 or 567 when looking at the time, license plate numbers, house numbers, receipts, book pages, or any other place numbers are used.⠀
⠀
Each number has its own vibrational frequency, carrying messages that we can interpret from the Divine. Save this post for the next time a sequence appears for you. What numbers do you most commonly see?

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sage Goddess on August 14, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and indoor.

node.text: If you've been waiting for a sign to join my online program in spiritual alchemy called Soul Shift, this post might be it 💙🌀💙 I've been teaching online classes in spirituality, aromatherapy, crystal healing, shamanism, and all aspects of sacred practice for a decade. But I've been a practitioner for 30 years and next month, in September, I'm taking you on a super deep dive to heal and activate the throat chakra. Never before in human history has it been more important to activate and heal your divine center of cosmic and spiritual expression. This experience is virtual and all of the classes are live and recorded for later viewing. There are no prerequisites. Come as you are. I have the tools, literally and metaphorically, to guide you. If you join the program now you won't miss a minute of the action in September. Head to sagegoddess.com/programs to register today, or just click the link in my bio. The tools in this photo are the class tools for September. To receive these in time, you have to register for the tools by midnight tonight, August 14. Come and journal with me, drum and journey with me, get inspired and grow with me. It may be the most important decision you make this year. And I would be honored to serve as your guide. See you in class! Please comment below if you're already joining me, and tag a friend who needs to know more about this opportunity.

node.text:

Swipe through to see a few of our newest offerings and make sure to use code ATHENA19 to save 19% if you're shopping 💎
